text:
Does it really matter what we call #cannabis?

Turns out yes, but not in the way you may expect.

An ongoing study found #cancer patients were more accepting of the  medical-sounding "#THC" and "Nabiximols" terms then either "cannabis" or "#marijuana" 🤔
